name: SUPER CRATE BOX FPS
body:
THIS IS GOING TO BE A 3D INTERPRETATION OF THE WACKY AND ADDICTIVE ARCADE EXPERIENCE BY VLAMBEER.

We are not affiliated with Vlambeer in any way, just thought this would be a mad idea.
tagline: A different interpretation of the awesome Vlambeer game.
